version_description: Neat accurate formatting, all lyrics including backing vocals with accompanying chords. Chord legend included.

The only other version of this song on the site is highly rated, but only puts chords above the first verse, and has some of the lyrics and chords wrong.
This is an incomplete cover of the Bob Dylan song. The main licks are played over the E Major Pentatonic Scale, so it's very easy once you've learned that.

The only other 'chord version there is all in block capitals, doesn't have chords over all of the verses, has lyrics missing, and has wrong chords in a few parts.  If a high enough mod reads this, I strongly recommend deleting the other...
